      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="43291320">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49317408/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u49317408-18.jpg" alt="Malisa" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43291320/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43291320/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49317408/" class=" " title="Malisa">Malisa</a>
                (愿不愿意和我一起养只白又白)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43291320">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们的记忆力不是把纯粹偶然的这一件事记住或者纯粹偶然的另一件事忘掉的机制，而是知道整理和瑞段舍弃的一种能力。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-04-21 16:27</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>我们的记忆力不是把纯粹偶然的这一件事记住或者纯粹偶然的另一件事忘掉的机制，而是知道整理和瑞段舍弃的一种能力。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43291320/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2017-04-21 16:27
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

    </div>
      <div class="ft">
        <p class="trr">&gt; <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1062343/annotation">更多读书笔记（共368篇）</a></p>
      </div>

